====Usage notes====
{{lang|ja|附}} is an alternative form of {{ja-l|付}}, which carries the meaning of {{l|en|enclosed}}/{{l|en|attached}}. Originally {{lang|ja|附}} was used for the intransitive verb {{ja-l|つく}}, while {{lang|ja|付}} served for the transitive {{ja-l|つける}}. Nowadays {{lang|ja|付}} is overwhelmingly used for both, with {{lang|ja|附}} having mostly fallen out of use entirely. However, it is still used sometimes in legal language and government-related terms.

